reviewText: Love it, as I do all of my virtual runs.

There's just something about these Virtual Active DVD's that make my treadmill run so much easier. This is my 4th one and just like the other three I have ( Los Angeles, Chicago and Sydney this one is great. I have a Treadmill that uses iFit also which is a service that uses Google maps with your treadmill, these DVDs to me are just as motivating. I'll have them all before its over....LOL
While I am indifferent to the Wellington part of this DVD, the Auckland is so fantastic I give this 5 stars.  In addition, the music is perfect cadence.
